8em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"_3-4-角度阈值判定\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_3-4-角度阈值判定\"><span>3.4 角度阈值判定</span></a></h3>\n<p>设最大允许角度差为 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>命中</mtext><mtext>  </mtext><mo>⟺</mo><mtext>  </mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><msup><mi>j</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup></msub><mo>≤</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{命中} \\iff \\Delta\\theta_{j^*} \\leq \\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7073em;vertical-align:-0.024em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">命中</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⟺</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9805em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3117em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6183em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.786em;margin-right:0.0714em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.5em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight\"><span class=\"mbin mtight\">∗</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≤</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>否则判定为未命中（miss）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"_3-5-角度阈值的必要性\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_3-5-角度阈值的必要性\"><span>3.5 角度阈值的必要性</span></a></h3>\n<p><strong>问题</strong>：外圈单词稀少（如只有 1–2 个），子弹只要落在该环内就必然命中，导致外圈单词被过度复习。</p>\n<p><strong>解决方案</strong>：引入 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，要求子弹必须落在单词的<strong>角度邻域</strong>内。</p>\n<p>设第 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\ell</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span></span></span></span> 环有 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 个单词，相邻单词角间距为 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2\\pi/n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span>。角度阈值 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 实际上限定了子弹的&quot;有效扇形区域&quot;面积，使得<strong>稀疏环中每个单词的实际命中概率</strong>正比于：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>P</mi><mtext>hit</mtext></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>∝</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>ring</mtext><mtext>  </mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><mi>π</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P_\\text{hit}(\\ell) \\propto P(\\text{ring}\\;\\ell) \\cdot \\frac{\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}}{\\pi}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">hit</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∝</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">ring</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0574em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3714em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>从而避免了稀疏环的过度命中。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">模式</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">适用场景</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">30°</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">严格</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">单词密度高，防止误命中</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">45°</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">平衡</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">通用默认</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">60°</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">宽松</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">单词数量少</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"附录-完整算法流程\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#附录-完整算法流程\"><span>附录：完整算法流程</span></a></h2>\n<div class=\"language- line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"language-\"><span class=\"line\"><span>输入：words（含 mastery）, N, w, σ, numBullets, Δθ_max</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>─── 阶段 1：单词坐标分配 ───────────────────────────────────────</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>for each word:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    ℓ = clamp(⌊m · N⌋, 0, N-1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    将 word 加入 rings[ℓ]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>for each ring ℓ:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    按 mastery 升序排列</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    for i, word in enumerate(rings[ℓ]):</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        θᵢ = (i / n) · 2π</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        r  = (ℓ + 0.5) · w</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        word.pos = (r·cos θᵢ, r·sin θᵢ)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>─── 阶段 2：子弹采样 ────────────────────────────────────────────</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>for _ in range(numBullets):</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    u₁, u₂ ~ Uniform(0, 1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    Z  = √(-2 ln u₁) · cos(2π u₂)    # Box-Muller</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    r_shot = σ · |Z|                   # 半正态极径</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    θ_shot ~ Uniform(0, 2π)            # 均匀极角</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    记录 (r_shot, θ_shot)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>─── 阶段 3：命中判定 ────────────────────────────────────────────</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>for each bullet (r_shot, θ_shot):</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    ℓ_shot = clamp(⌊r_shot / w⌋, 0, N-1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    candidates = rings[ℓ_shot] \\ already_hit</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    if candidates is empty: continue</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    j* = argmin_j Δθ(j, shot)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    if Δθ(j*, shot) ≤ Δθ_max:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        hit(j*)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>输出：hitWords, missCount</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><hr>\n<h2 id=\"符号表\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#符号表\"><span>符号表</span></a></h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">符号</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">含义</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">默认值</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">单词熟练度</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\in [0,1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">N</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">总环数</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">环宽</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">3.0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\ell</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">环级</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>σ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\sigma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">σ</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">半正态分布参数</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">9.0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>max</mtext></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta\\theta_\\text{max}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">max</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">最大角度差阈值</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">45°</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">环内单词数</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n","env":{"base":"/","filePath":"C:/Users/29657/vuepress-starter/docs/algorithm.md","filePathRelative":"algorithm.md","frontmatter":{"title":"VocabShoot 核心算法文档","permalink":"/algorithm/","createTime":"2026/03/29 14:51:33"},"sfcBlocks":{"template":{"type":"template","content":"<template><h1 id=\"vocabshoot-核心算法文档\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#vocabshoot-核心算法文档\"><span>VocabShoot 核心算法文档</span></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>本文档系统阐述 VocabShoot 三个核心算法模块的数学原理与推导过程。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"目录\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#目录\"><span>目录</span></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D\">单词坐标分配</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%B9%E8%90%BD%E7%82%B9%E9%87%87%E6%A0%B7\">子弹落点采样</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%B9%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A\">子弹命中判定</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"_1-单词坐标分配\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_1-单词坐标分配\"><span>1 单词坐标分配</span></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"_1-1-设计目标\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_1-1-设计目标\"><span>1.1 设计目标</span></a></h3>\n<p>将词库中每个单词映射到极坐标系的某个位置，使得<strong>熟练度越低的单词越靠近中心</strong>，便于后续采样时以更高概率命中它们。</p>\n<h3 id=\"_1-2-环级映射\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_1-2-环级映射\"><span>1.2 环级映射</span></a></h3>\n<p>给定单词熟练度 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m \\in [0, 1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 与总环数 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">N</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span></span></span></span>，定义<strong>环级</strong>：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">⌊</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>N</mi><mo fence=\"true\">⌋</mo></mrow><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mspace width=\"1em\"/><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>N</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\ell = \\left\\lfloor m \\cdot N \\right\\rfloor, \\quad \\ell \\in \\{0, 1, \\ldots, N-1\\}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">⌊</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">⌋</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:1em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">ℓ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\">…</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>特别地，当 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m = 1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 时需截断到 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>N</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">N-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"ma