s=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3448em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.3488em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.0714em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.5em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">shot</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1512em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2559em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>（排除已命中单词），计算<strong>圆周角度差</strong>（考虑 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2\\pi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span></span></span></span> 周期性）：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mtext> ⁣</mtext><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>shot</mtext></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mtext> </mtext><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mtext>shot</mtext></msub><mi mathvariant=