ight:0.05724em;\">j</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord text mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">shot</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>选取角度差最小的单词：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>j</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>arg</mi><mo>⁡</mo><munder><mrow><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>j</mi><mo>∈</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=\"script\">W</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℓ</mi><mtext>shot</mtext></msub></msub></mrow></munder><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>j</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">j^* = \\arg\\min_{j \\in \\mathcal{W}_{\\ell_\\text{shot}}} \\Delta\\theta_j\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9331em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;